    public final class MapEditorTransformPanel
extends FreeColPanel
    A panel for choosing the current MapTransform.

    This panel is only used when running in map editor mode.
    See Also:
    MapEditorController.getMapTransform(), MapEditorTransformPanel.MapTransform, Serialized Form
